Insider Activity


Individual




Eric C. Scroggins



Mr. Eric C. Scroggins is Secretary, Vice President & General Counsel at Allison Transmission Holdings, Inc. and Secretary, Vice President & General Counsel at Allison Transmission, Inc.
Mr. Scroggins was previously employed as General Counsel by Product Action International LLC, Attorney by Ice Miller Donadio & Ryan, and Deputy Director-Indiana State Personnel Department by State of Indiana.



